src: Ford accepts the fait accompli with good grace.
mt: Ford aksepterer det fullbyrdede faktum med god mine.
backtranslation: Ford accepts the fait accompli with a straight face.

src: Falstaff, pleased to find himself not the only dupe, proclaims that all the world is folly, and all are figures of fun ("Tutto nel mondo è burla... Tutti gabbati!... Ma ride ben chi ride La risata final." / "Everything in the world is a jest... but he laughs well who laughs the final laugh").
mt: Falstaff, glad for å finne ut at han ikke er det eneste offeret, erklærer at hele verden er tåpelighet, og alle er latterlige figurer ("Tutto nel mondo è burla... Tutti gabbati!... Ma ride ben chi ride La risata final." / "Alt i verden er en spøk... men den som ler sist, ler best").
backtranslation: Falstaff, happy to find out that he is not the only victim, declares that the whole world is foolishness, and everyone is ridiculous characters ("Tutto nel mondo è burla... Tutti gabbati!... Ma ride ben chi ride La risata final." / "Everything in the world is a joke... but he who laughs last, laughs best").

src: The entire company repeats his proclamation in an exuberant ten-voice fugue.
mt: Hele ensemblet gjentar hans proklamasjon i en sprudlende fuge for ti stemmer.
backtranslation: The entire ensemble repeats his proclamation in an exuberant fugue for ten voices.

src: They won all their group matches to finish top of the pool.
mt: De vant alle gruppespillkampene sine og endte dermed på toppen av gruppen.
backtranslation: They won all their group stage matches and ended up at the top of the group.

src: After defeating France in the quarter-finals, they lost to the eventual tournament winners South Africa in the semi-finals.
mt: Etter å ha slått Frankrike i kvartfinalen, tapte de mot de endelige turneringsvinnerne Sør-Afrika i semifinalen.
backtranslation: After beating France in the quarterfinals, they lost to eventual tournament winners South Africa in the semifinals.

src: The arrangement of Thiele and Ladiges was not accepted by George, and was discarded in his 1999 revision.
mt: Thiele og Ladiges' ordning ble ikke akseptert av George, og ble forkastet i hans revisjon fra 1999.
backtranslation: Thiele and Ladiges' scheme was not accepted by George, and was rejected in his 1999 revision.

src: Under George's 1999 arrangement, B. epica's placement was as follows:
mt: I henhold til Georges ordning fra 1999 var plasseringen av B. epica som følger:
backtranslation: According to George's 1999 scheme, the placement of B. epica was as follows:

src: The Outsider also grants his mark, and special abilities, to other characters.
mt: Outsideren gir også sitt merke, og spesielle evner, til andre karakterer.
backtranslation: The outsider also lends their brand, and special abilities, to other characters.

src: Smith described the character as an amoral figure who grants abilities, but leaves the choice of how to use them up to the recipient.
mt: Smith beskrev karakteren som en amoralisk figur som gir evner, men lar mottakeren bestemme hvordan de skal brukes.
backtranslation: Smith described the character as an amoral figure who gives abilities but lets the recipient decide how to use them.

src: Devil May Cry begins with Dante (Drew Coombs) being attacked in his office by a mysterious woman named Trish (Sara Lafleur).
mt: Devil May Cry begynner med at Dante (Drew Coombs) blir angrepet på kontoret sitt av en mystisk kvinne ved navn Trish (Sara Lafleur).
backtranslation: Devil May Cry begins with Dante (Drew Coombs) being attacked in his office by a mysterious woman named Trish (Sara Lafleur).

src: He impresses her by easily brushing off her assault, and explains that for years, he has hunted demons in pursuit of the ones who killed his mother and brother.
mt: Han imponerer henne ved å lett avverge angrepet hennes, og forklarer at han i årevis har jaktet på demoner i jakten på de som drepte moren og broren hans.
backtranslation: He impresses her by easily fending off her attack, explaining that he has spent years hunting demons in pursuit of those who killed his mother and brother.

src: Trish explains that her attack was a test, and that the demon emperor Mundus (Tony Daniels), whom Dante holds responsible for the deaths of his family, is planning to cross over into the human world after centuries of imprisonment.
mt: Trish forklarer at angrepet hennes var en test, og at demonkeiseren Mundus (Tony Daniels), som Dante holder ansvarlig for familiens død, planlegger å krysse over til menneskenes verden etter århundrer i fangenskap.
backtranslation: Trish explains that her attack was a test and that the demon emperor Mundus (Tony Daniels), whom Dante holds responsible for his family's death, is planning to cross over to the human world after centuries in captivity.

src: Rainbow is a documentary filmmaker.
mt: Rainbow er en dokumentarfilmskaper.
backtranslation: Rainbow is a documentary filmmaker.

src: Liz O'Rourke says she is now working with the mentally disabled (although she is later revealed to be a midwife in the episode "Father Figure").
mt: Liz O'Rourke sier at hun nå jobber med psykisk utviklingshemmede (selv om det senere i episoden «Father Figure» avsløres at hun er jordmor).
backtranslation: Liz O'Rourke says she now works with the mentally disabled (although later in the episode "Father Figure" it is revealed that she is a midwife).

src: Trish Skye says she had problems but has been clean and sober for two years; she works at a funeral home and is a freelance writer.
mt: Trish Skye sier at hun hadde problemer, men har vært rusfri i to år. Hun jobber på et begravelsesbyrå og er frilansskribent.
backtranslation: Trish Skye says she had problems, but has been drug-free for two years. She works at a funeral home and is a freelance writer.

src: Before joining Bernard in Paris, Rosa stays in a flat in London for several weeks.
mt: Før Rosa slår seg sammen med Bernard i Paris, bor hun i en leilighet i London i flere uker.
backtranslation: Before Rosa joins Bernard in Paris, she lives in a flat in London for several weeks.

src: Now that she has no intention of honouring the agreement of her passport, which was to return to South Africa within a year, she openly introduces herself as Burger's daughter.
mt: Nå som hun ikke har noen intensjon om å overholde avtalen i passet sitt, som var å returnere til Sør-Afrika innen et år, presenterer hun seg åpent som Burgers datter.
backtranslation: Now that she has no intention of honoring the agreement in her passport, which was to return to South Africa within a year, she openly introduces herself as Burger's daughter.

src: This attracts the attention of the media and she attends several political events.
mt: Dette tiltrekker seg medienes oppmerksomhet, og hun deltar på flere politiske arrangementer.
backtranslation: This attracts media attention, and she participates in several political events.

src: Following Roy Hodgson's appointment, The Sun mocked his rhotacism manner of speech with a "Bwing on the Euwos!" front-page headline.
mt: Etter at Roy Hodgson ble utnevnt, spottet The Sun hans rhotasisme med en forsideoverskrift som lød: «Bwing on the Euwos!»
backtranslation: After Roy Hodgson was appointed, The Sun mocked his rhotasism with a front page headline that read: "Bwing on the Euwos!"

src: The FA called the headline "unacceptable" and more than 100 people complained to the Press Complaints Commission.
mt: FA kalte overskriften «uakseptabel», og over 100 personer klaget til Pressens klagenemnd.
backtranslation: The FA called the headline "unacceptable", and more than 100 people complained to the Press Complaints Board.

src: As a response to this, in 2017 boats off the British Columbia coast now have a minimum approach distance of 200 metres compared to the previous 100 metres.
mt: Som svar på dette har båter utenfor kysten av Britisk Columbia i 2017 nå en minimumstilnærmingsavstand på 200 meter, sammenlignet med de tidligere 100 meterne.
backtranslation: In response, in 2017, boats off the coast of British Columbia now have a minimum approach distance of 200 meters, compared to the previous 100 meters.

src: This new rule complements Washington State's minimum approach zone of 180 metres that has been in effect since 2011.
mt: Denne nye regelen utfyller Washington States minimumstilnærmingssone på 180 meter som har vært gjeldende siden 2011.
backtranslation: This new rule complements Washington State's minimum approach zone of 180 meters that has been in effect since 2011.

src: If a whale approaches a vessel it must be placed in neutral until the whale passes.
mt: Hvis en hval nærmer seg et fartøy, må fartøyet settes i nøytral posisjon til hvalen har passert.
backtranslation: If a whale approaches a vessel, the vessel must be put in neutral position until the whale has passed.

src: A number of locations in and around Dallas were used in production.
mt: En rekke steder i og rundt Dallas ble brukt under produksjonen.
backtranslation: A number of locations in and around Dallas were used during production.

src: An office in Renaissance Tower was used for the OCP interior of; the company's exterior is Dallas City Hall, modified with matte paintings to appear taller.
mt: Et kontor i Renaissance Tower ble brukt til OCPs interiør; selskapets eksteriør er Dallas rådhus, modifisert med matte malerier for å virke høyere.
backtranslation: An office in the Renaissance Tower was used for OCP's interior; the company's exterior is Dallas City Hall, modified with matte paintings to appear taller.

src: The OCP elevator was that of the Plaza of the Americas.
mt: OCP-heisen var den som tilhørte Plaza of the Americas.
backtranslation: The OCP elevator was the one that belonged to Plaza of the Americas.

src: Although the traditional accounts are in agreement that Lydda almost immediately fell into obscurity following the founding of Ramla, narratives vary about the extent of Sulayman's efforts to transfer Lydda's inhabitants to Ramla, some holding that he only demolished a church in Lydda and others that he demolished the city altogether.
mt: Selv om de tradisjonelle beretningene er enige om at Lydda nesten umiddelbart falt i glemsel etter grunnleggelsen av Ramla, varierer fortellingene om omfanget av Sulaymans innsats for å overføre Lyddas innbyggere til Ramla. Noen hevder at han bare rev en kirke i Lydda, mens andre mener at han rev byen fullstendig.
backtranslation: Although the traditional accounts agree that Lydda almost immediately fell into oblivion after the founding of Ramla, accounts vary as to the extent of Sulayman's efforts to transfer Lydda's inhabitants to Ramla. Some claim that he only demolished a church in Lydda, while others believe that he demolished the town completely.

src: Al-Ya'qubi (d. 839) noted Sulayman razed the houses of Lydda's inhabitants to force their relocation to Ramla and punished those who resisted.
mt: Al-Ya'qubi (d. 839) bemerket at Sulayman raserte husene til innbyggerne i Lydda for å tvinge dem til å flytte til Ramla og straffet de som gjorde motstand.
backtranslation: Al-Ya'qubi (d. 839) noted that Sulayman razed the houses of the inhabitants of Lydda to force them to move to Ramla and punished those who resisted.

src: In the words of al-Jahshiyari, Sulayman "founded the town of al-Ramla and its mosque and thus caused the ruin of Lod
mt: Med al-Jahshiyaris ord grunnla Sulayman «byen al-Ramla og dens moské og forårsaket dermed ødeleggelsen av Lod».
backtranslation: In the words of al-Jahshiyari, Sulayman "founded the city of al-Ramla and its mosque, thus causing the destruction of Lod".

src: Rolling Stone includes the album and several songs on various "best of" lists, such as:
mt: Rolling Stone inkluderer albumet og flere sanger på diverse «beste av»-lister, som for eksempel:
backtranslation: Rolling Stone includes the album and several songs on various "best of" lists, such as:

src: The Tactical Patrol Force (TPF) of the New York City Police Department arrived to free the police trapped inside the Stonewall.
mt: Den taktiske patruljestyrken (TPF) til New York City Police Department ankom for å befri politiet som var fanget inne i Stonewall.
backtranslation: The Tactical Patrol Force (TPF) of the New York City Police Department arrived to free the police trapped inside Stonewall.

src: One officer's eye was cut and a few others were bruised from being struck by flying debris.
mt: En politibetjent fikk et kutt i øyet, og noen få andre fikk blåmerker etter å ha blitt truffet av flygende gjenstander.
backtranslation: One police officer suffered a cut to his eye and a few others suffered bruises after being hit by flying objects.

src: Bob Kohler, who was walking his dog by the Stonewall that night, saw the TPF arrive:
mt: Bob Kohler, som luftet hunden sin ved Stonewall den kvelden, så TPF ankomme:
backtranslation: Bob Kohler, who was walking his dog at Stonewall that night, saw TPF arrive:

src: Waziri and Afonja save Tawa.
mt: Waziri og Afonja redder Tawa.
backtranslation: Waziri and Afonja rescue Tawa.

src: Waziri subsequently presents his account of the investigation to the British, who instruct him to withhold Aderopo's identity; he reluctantly agrees to do so for the sake of a peaceful independence.
mt: Waziri presenterer deretter sin beretning om etterforskningen til britene, som instruerer ham om å holde Aderopos identitet hemmelig. Han går motvillig med på å gjøre det for en fredelig uavhengighet.
backtranslation: Waziri then presents his account of the investigation to the British, who instruct him to keep Aderopo's identity secret. He reluctantly agrees to do so for the sake of peaceful independence.

src: Diller planned on a new Star Trek series forming the cornerstone for a new television network.
mt: Diller planla en ny Star Trek-serie som skulle danne hjørnesteinen for et nytt TV-nettverk.
backtranslation: Diller was planning a new Star Trek series that would form the cornerstone of a new TV network.

src: Though Paramount was reluctant to abandon its work on the film, Roddenberry wanted to bring many of the production staff from the original series to work on the new show, titled Star Trek: Phase II.
mt: Selv om Paramount var motvillige til å gi opp arbeidet med filmen, ønsket Roddenberry å ta med seg mange av produksjonsmedarbeiderne fra den originale serien for å jobbe med den nye serien, med tittelen Star Trek: Phase II.
backtranslation: Although Paramount was reluctant to give up work on the film, Roddenberry wanted to bring back many of the production staff from the original series to work on the new series, entitled Star Trek: Phase II.

src: Chilean devil ray (M. tarapacana)
mt: Chilensk djevelrokke (M. tarapacana)
backtranslation: Chilean manta ray (M. tarapacana)

src: Cory Edwards chose to approach the film predominantly as an action/comedy, instead of as a typical animated film, and wrote the script to appeal to audiences of any age like many of the films produced by Pixar or Disney.
mt: Cory Edwards valgte å tilnærme seg filmen hovedsakelig som en action/komedie, i stedet for som en typisk animasjonsfilm, og skrev manuset for å appellere til publikum i alle aldre, slik som mange av filmene produsert av Pixar eller Disney.
backtranslation: Cory Edwards chose to approach the film primarily as an action/comedy, rather than a typical animated film, and wrote the script to appeal to audiences of all ages, like many of the films produced by Pixar or Disney.

src: Bugs Bunny, Road Runner, The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle and Friends, The Muppets, The Simpsons and The Incredibles (2004) have all been cited as inspirations for the film.
mt: Bugs Bunny, Road Runner, The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle and Friends, The Muppets, The Simpsons og The Incredibles (2004) har alle blitt nevnt som inspirasjonskilder for filmen.
backtranslation: Bugs Bunny, Road Runner, The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle and Friends, The Muppets, The Simpsons and The Incredibles (2004) have all been cited as inspirations for the film.

src: By the early 1930s, Orizaba's typical route had remained virtually the same, though Nassau and Tampico were dropped as ports of call.
mt: Tidlig på 1930-tallet var Orizabas typiske rute praktisk talt den samme, selv om Nassau og Tampico ble droppet som anløpshavner.
backtranslation: In the early 1930s, Orizaba's typical route was virtually the same, although Nassau and Tampico were dropped as ports of call.

src: It was in this period that American poet Hart Crane leapt to his death from Orizaba.
mt: Det var i denne perioden den amerikanske poeten Hart Crane hoppet i døden fra Orizaba.
backtranslation: It was during this period that the American poet Hart Crane jumped to his death from Orizaba.

src: At around noon on 27 April 1932, while the ship was headed to New York—some 275 miles (443 km) north of Havana and 10 miles (16 km) off the Florida coast—Crane, clad in pajamas and overcoat, climbed the rail at the stern of the ship and plunged into the ocean.
mt: Rundt middagstid den 27. april 1932, mens skipet var på vei til New York – omtrent 443 km nord for Havana og 16 km utenfor Floridas kyst – klatret Crane, iført pyjamas og frakk, over rekka akterut på skipet og stupte ut i havet.
backtranslation: Around noon on April 27, 1932, while the ship was en route to New York - about 443 km north of Havana and 16 km off the coast of Florida - Crane, wearing pajamas and a coat, climbed over the railing at the stern of the ship and plunged into the sea.

src: How you use your eyes, your position, and how you maximize camera angles... I didn't know those things before."
mt: Hvordan du bruker øynene dine, posisjonen din og hvordan du maksimerer kameravinklene ... Jeg visste ikke de tingene før.
backtranslation: How to use your eyes, your position and how to maximize camera angles... I didn't know those things before.

src: To prepare for the role of a courtesan, she learned different styles of ballroom dances and trained in pole dance for three months.
mt: For å forberede seg til rollen som kurtisane, lærte hun seg forskjellige stiler av selskapsdans og trente poledans i tre måneder.
backtranslation: To prepare for her role as a courtesan, she learned different styles of ballroom dancing and practiced pole dancing for three months.

src: Critic Julia
mt: Kritikeren Julia
backtranslation: Critics Julia

src: On August 26, George H. W. Bush toured devastated areas of Louisiana with Governor Edwin Edwards.
mt: Den 26. august besøkte George H.W. Bush ødelagte områder i Louisiana sammen med guvernør Edwin Edwards.
backtranslation: On August 26, George H.W. Bush visited devastated areas in Louisiana together with Governor Edwin Edwards.

src: President Bush remarked, "The destruction from this storm goes beyond anything we have known in recent years," but noted that damage was less severe than in Florida.
mt: President Bush bemerket: «Ødeleggelsene fra denne stormen overgår alt vi har sett de siste årene», men bemerket at skadene var mindre alvorlige enn i Florida.
backtranslation: President Bush remarked: "The devastation from this storm surpasses anything we've seen in recent years," but noted that the damage was less severe than in Florida.

src: After his visit to Louisiana, President Bush declared only Terrebonne Parish as a disaster area, but later included 34 other parishes under this declaration.
mt: Etter besøket i Louisiana erklærte president Bush bare Terrebonne Parish som katastrofeområde, men inkluderte senere 34 andre menigheter under denne erklæringen.
backtranslation: After his visit to Louisiana, President Bush declared only Terrebonne Parish a disaster area, but later included 34 other parishes under this declaration.

src: When general elections were held in July 2003, the CPP won, while FUNCINPEC polled 20.8 percent of the popular vote and secured 26 out of a total of 120 parliamentary seats.
mt: Da det ble holdt parlamentsvalg i juli 2003, vant CPP, mens FUNCINPEC fikk 20,8 prosent av stemmene og sikret seg 26 av totalt 120 parlamentsseter.
backtranslation: When parliamentary elections were held in July 2003, the CPP won, while FUNCINPEC received 20.8 percent of the votes and secured 26 of a total of 120 parliamentary seats.

src: This marked an 11 percentage point drop in FUNCINPEC's share of the popular vote compared with 1998.
mt: Dette markerte en nedgang på 11 prosentpoeng i FUNCINPECs andel av de avgitte stemmene sammenlignet med 1998.
backtranslation: This marked a decrease of 11 percentage points in FUNCINPEC's share of the votes cast compared to 1998.

src: Palaces are usually arranged around one or more courtyards, with their façades facing inwards; some examples are adorned with sculpture.
mt: Slott er vanligvis anordnet rundt en eller flere gårdsplasser, med fasadene vendt innover; noen eksempler er utsmykket med skulpturer.
backtranslation: Castles are usually arranged around one or more courtyards, with the facades facing inwards; some examples are adorned with sculptures.

src: Some palaces possess associated hieroglyphic descriptions that identify them as the royal residences of named rulers.
mt: Noen palasser har tilhørende hieroglyfiske beskrivelser som identifiserer dem som de kongelige residensene til navngitte herskere.
backtranslation: Some palaces have accompanying hieroglyphic descriptions identifying them as the royal residences of named rulers.

src: The Inquisition post mortem held after Minsterworth's execution casts light upon his land-holding, much of which was held directly off John of Gaunt, son of King Edward III.
mt: Inquisitio post mortem som ble holdt etter Minsterworths henrettelse, kaster lys over hans jordeiendom, hvorav mye ble holdt direkte av John av Gaunt, sønn av kong Edward III.
backtranslation: The inquisitio post mortem held after Minsterworth's execution sheds light on his landed property, much of which was held directly by John of Gaunt, son of King Edward III.

src: This was particularly concentrated in the southwest of England.
mt: Dette var spesielt konsentrert i det sørvestlige England.
backtranslation: This was particularly concentrated in the South West of England.

src: Daniel feels ignored by his father, who has chosen Alexis to be his best man.
mt: Daniel føler seg ignorert av faren sin, som har valgt Alexis til å være forloveren sin.
backtranslation: Daniel feels ignored by his father, who has chosen Alexis to be his best man.

src: Christina McKinney (Ashley Jensen), MODE's seamstress, reunites with her husband Stuart (Derek Riddell) after leaving him in Scotland years ago; he reveals he is dying of a rare disease which requires a $100,000 operation.
mt: Christina McKinney (Ashley Jensen), MODE sin syerske, gjenforenes med ektemannen Stuart (Derek Riddell) etter å ha forlatt ham i Skottland for flere år siden. Han avslører at han er døende av en sjelden sykdom som krever en operasjon til 100 000 dollar.
backtranslation: Christina McKinney (Ashley Jensen), MODE's seamstress, reunites with her husband Stuart (Derek Riddell) after leaving him in Scotland several years ago. He reveals that he is dying of a rare disease that requires a $100,000 operation.

src: Mistress Quickly rushes in, shouting that Ford has returned home unexpectedly with a retinue of henchmen to catch his wife's lover.
mt: Fru Quickly stormer inn og roper at Ford har kommet uventet hjem med en gruppe håndlangere for å fange konas elsker.
backtranslation: Mrs. Quickly storms in, shouting that Ford has come home unexpectedly with a group of henchmen to capture his wife's lover.

src: Falstaff hides first behind the screen, but realizes that Ford will likely look for him there.
mt: Falstaff gjemmer seg først bak skjermen, men innser at Ford sannsynligvis vil lete etter ham der.
backtranslation: Falstaff initially hides behind the screen, but realizes that Ford will probably look for him there.

src: The women urge him to hide in the laundry basket, which he does.
mt: Kvinnene oppfordrer ham til å gjemme seg i vaskekurven, noe han gjør.
backtranslation: The women encourage him to hide in the laundry basket, which he does.

src: In that year he was seen by Arthur Sullivan and, separately, by W. S. Gilbert, in performances of their one-act comic opera Trial by Jury.
mt: I det året ble han sett av Arthur Sullivan og, separat, av W. S. Gilbert, i opptredener av deres enakter komiske opera Trial by Jury.
backtranslation: In that year he was seen by Arthur Sullivan and, separately, by W. S. Gilbert, in performances of their one-act comic opera Trial by Jury.

src: Impressed, they engaged him to play the comic lead in their new, full-length work, The Sorcerer.
mt: Imponert engasjerte de ham til å spille den komiske hovedrollen i deres nye helaftens verk, Trollmannen.
backtranslation: Impressed, they hired him to play the comic lead in their new full-length work, The Wizard.

src: Thereafter, Grossmith created the leading comic role in each of Gilbert and Sullivan's long-running comic operas until The Yeomen of the Guard, which closed in 1889.
mt: Deretter skapte Grossmith den ledende komiske rollen i hver av Gilbert og Sullivans langvarige komiske operaer frem til The Yeomen of the Guard, som ble avsluttet i 1889.
backtranslation: Subsequently, Grossmith created the leading comic role in each of Gilbert and Sullivan's long-running comic operas until The Yeomen of the Guard, which was completed in 1889.

src: While returning home, Sudeep kidnaps and strangles Nani to death, making his death look like an accident.
mt: På vei hjem kidnapper og kveler Sudeep Nani til døde, og får det til å se ut som en ulykke.
backtranslation: On his way home, Sudeep kidnaps and strangles Nani to death, making it look like an accident.

src: Before dying, Nani curses Sudeep, swearing to kill Sudeep if he tries to hurt Bindu.
mt: Før hun dør, forbanner Nani Sudeep og sverger på å drepe ham hvis han prøver å skade Bindu.
backtranslation: Before she dies, Nani curses Sudeep and vows to kill him if he tries to hurt Bindu.

src: Unaware of the incident, Bindu confesses her love for the dying Nani by phone; it is the last thing Nani hears before he dies.
mt: Uvitende om hendelsen, tilstår Bindu sin kjærlighet til den døende Nani via telefon; det er det siste Nani hører før han dør.
backtranslation: Unaware of the incident, Bindu confesses his love to the dying Nani over the phone; it's the last thing Nani hears before he dies.

src: When Amir does not return, Tati and her aunt are worried: as Tati saw Amir with Omi, she fears that the two have run away together.
mt: Når Amir ikke kommer tilbake, blir Tati og tanten hennes bekymret: siden Tati så Amir sammen med Omi, frykter hun at de to har stukket av sammen.
backtranslation: When Amir doesn't return, Tati and her aunt get worried: since Tati saw Amir with Omi, she fears that the two have run away together.

src: Heartbroken, she intends to return to Cigading.
mt: Med knust hjerte har hun til hensikt å vende tilbake til Cigading.
backtranslation: With a broken heart, she intends to return to Cigading.

src: The rare formal social events in the Pooters' lives are particular magnets for misfortune.
mt: De sjeldne formelle sosiale begivenhetene i Pooters' liv er spesielle magneter for uflaks.
backtranslation: The rare formal social events in Pooters' lives are special magnets for bad luck.

src: They receive an invitation from the Lord Mayor of London to attend a ball at the Mansion House for "Representatives of Trade and Commerce".
mt: De mottar en invitasjon fra Londons ordfører om å delta på et ball i Mansion House for «representanter for handel og næringsliv».
backtranslation: They receive an invitation from the Mayor of London to attend a ball at the Mansion House for "representatives of trade and industry".

src: †Mammuthus primigenius (woolly mammoth)
mt: †Mammuthus primigenius (ullmammut)
backtranslation: †Mammuthus primigenius (mammoth)
